  "title": "KEY ACCOUNTS MANAGER (SALES) - POSSESS OWN VEHICLE",
  "description": "<p><strong>• Up to $66,000 per Annum</strong></p><p><strong>• Basic Salary: Up to $3,500 + $400 Transport + $100 Mobile + $700 Petrol Card</strong></p><p><strong>• Entitled to fixed AWS + Variable bonus</strong></p><p><strong>• High yearly incentive based on performance</strong></p><p><strong>• Must possess own vehicle - Car or Bike</strong><br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Reporting to the Head of Sales, implement sales strategies to grow revenue in the Electrical Product Segment, Smart Home System & Ecommerce platform</p></li><li><p>Building rapport with Key Account Clients</p></li><li><p>Achieve Sales target with existing or new clients by working with Electrical Contractors, M&E Consultants, Interior Designers, Architects & residential owners<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li><p>At least 1 year sales experience</p></li><li><p>Must possess own vehicle - Car or bike<br /></p></li></ul><p>Kindly email your resume in a detailed Word format to<br /></p><p><a href=\"mailto:roy.yeo@peopleprofilers.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">roy.yeo@peopleprofilers.com</a><br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</p><p>People Profilers Pte Ltd</p><p>20 Cecil Street, #08-09 PLUS Building Singapore 049705</p><p>EA License Number: 02C4944</p><p>Registration Number: R1217882</p><p>Posting Personnel: Yeo Yi Rong</p><p>Tel: <a href=\"tel:6950 9757\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">6950 9757</a></p>",
